snippet.title: The Expanse: A Telltale Series - Official Behind-The-Scenes Trailer
snippet.description: Join members of the teams at Deck Nine and Telltale for a deep dive into The Expanse: A Telltale Series, including the creative process and how they created a game true to The Expanse sci-fi universe. The Expanse: A Telltale Series Episode 1 will be available in summer 2023.
